1. *Account Management*:
<br>
   - Create new accounts
<br>
   - Login with account number and password
<br>

2. *Banking Operations*:
<br>
   - Deposit money
<br>
   - Withdraw money
<br>
   - Transfer money to other accounts
<br>
   - View transaction history
<br>

3. *Security*:
<br>
   - Password protection for accounts
<br>
   - Input validation
<br>

4. *User Interface*:
<br>
   - Simple text-based menu system
<br>
   - Clear display of account information
